34:09.390 --> 34:10.550
- OKAY, OKAY, YOU READY?
- YES.

34:10.600 --> 34:12.147
- ALL RIGHT. OKAY.
- ALL RIGHT.

34:12.180 --> 34:13.590
- NO, I GO BACK THERE.

34:13.630 --> 34:15.313
YOU GO IN FRONT.
- ALL RIGHT. OKAY.

34:15.360 --> 34:17.248
ALL RIGHT.
- OH, HERE WE GO.

34:17.290 --> 34:19.850
- WELCOME,
LADIES AND GENTLEMEN,

34:19.880 --> 34:21.495
BOYS AND GIRLS.

34:21.540 --> 34:23.292
IT IS MY DEEPEST PLEASURE
TO PRESENT

34:23.330 --> 34:26.777
A MAN WHO KNOWS SO MUCH
ABOUT BUGS--

34:26.820 --> 34:30.165
BUGS OF ALL KINDS.

34:30.200 --> 34:32.191
