- WELCOME.
I AM THE AMAZING ANDY.

35:04.610 --> 35:06.373
AND I WANT TO WELCOME YOU

35:06.410 --> 35:09.789
TO AMAZING AN DY'S
WONDERFUL WORLD OF BUGS.

35:09.830 --> 35:11.718
WHEN I SAY THE WORD "BUG,"

35:11.760 --> 35:14.615
YOU THINK OF SOMETHING CREEPY
AND SCARY.

35:14.660 --> 35:16.935
- RIGHT?
- HA.

35:16.970 --> 35:19.245
- I'LL HAVE TO HAVE THAT BACK.
