35:20.630 --> 35:24.498
I'D LIKE EVERYBODY
TO BE VERY STILL AND QUIET.

35:24.530 --> 35:26.418
[kids talking softly]

35:26.460 --> 35:28.257
THIS IS THE LARGEST SPIDER
IN MY COLLECTION.

35:28.290 --> 35:30.599
WHAT YOU MAY NOT KNOW

35:30.640 --> 35:32.153
IS THAT ON YOUR OWN CONTINENT

35:32.190 --> 35:34.226
OF NORTH AMERICA--
- THERE ARE OVER 30 SPECIES.

35:34.270 --> 35:36.363
- THERE ARE AS MANY
AS 30 SPECIES.

35:36.410 --> 35:38.162
- AND SOME OF THEM
HAVE TOXIC BITES.

35:38.200 --> 35:40.680
- EXACTLY. NO COMMENTS
FROM THE AUDIENCE, PLEASE.

35:40.720 --> 35:43.757
I HOPE HE DOESN'T GET AWAY
AND JOIN YOU IN THE AUDIENCE.

35:43.790 --> 35:45.405
- [laughs]
ANDY.

35:45.450 --> 35:47.543
- I HOPE HE DOES.
- HOW'S IT GOING?

35:47.590 --> 35:48.898
- IT'S GOING VERY WELL.

35:48.930 --> 35:50.318
- GOOD.

35:50.350 --> 35:51.658
- AMAZING ANDY IS ACTUALLY...

35:51.700 --> 35:53.759
- YOU SEE, IT'S MUCH BIGGER
THAN THE COCKROACHES

35:53.800 --> 35:55.415
AT YOUR HOUSE,
WHICH I HOPE YOU DON'T HAVE ANY.

35:55.460 --> 35:58.247
- QUITE AMAZING.
- MM.

35:58.290 --> 35:59.427
- THAT'S THE MADAGASCAR
HISSING COCKROACH.

35:59.460 --> 36:02.702
- THIS IS A MADAGASCAR
HISSING COCKROACH.

36:02.740 --> 36:06.187
WHEN HE'S THREATENED,
HE CAN SQUEEZE AIR OUT

36:06.230 --> 36:07.436
THROUGH THEIR EXOSKELETON.
IT MAKES A LOUD--

36:07.470 --> 36:09.222
- HISSING SOUND.
- [hisses]

36:09.270 --> 36:10.191
[all gasping]

36:10.230 --> 36:11.299
- THAT'S NOT
WHAT IT SOUNDS LIKE AT ALL.

36:11.340 --> 36:13.433
IT'S MORE LIKE A...

36:13.480 --> 36:16.199
- THIS IS THE BEST BUG SHOW
I'VE EVER SEEN.

36:16.240 --> 36:17.616
- THIS IS A PRESERVED SPECIMEN

36:17.650 --> 36:18.992
OF THE HERCULES BEETLE.

36:19.030 --> 36:20.759
HAVE YOU HEARD OF THAT?
YOU CAN TELL THIS IS A MALE,

36:20.790 --> 36:24.658
'CAUSE IT HAS THIS LONG HORN
ON THE FRONT OF IT.

36:24.690 --> 36:28.239
- WHAT'S UP?
- NOTHING.

36:28.280 --> 36:29.554
THEY WERE JUST BANGING
IN THE BATHROOM.

36:29.600 --> 36:31.807
- WHO?
- JOEL AND JULIA WERE HAVING SEX

36:31.840 --> 36:32.977
IN OUR BATHROOM.
HONEY, DON'T.

36:33.010 --> 36:33.874
DON'T EMBARRASS THEM.

36:33.910 --> 36:36.663
- THAT'S THE EQUIVALENT
OF A HUMAN BEING

36:36.710 --> 36:40.259
LIFTING UP TWO SHERMAN TANKS
UP IN THE AIR.

36:40.300 --> 36:41.949
all: WOW.
- IT'S KIND OF EXCITING, THOUGH.

36:41.990 --> 36:44.333
I MEAN, YOU KNOW,
WHAT IF A CHILD IS CONCEIVED

36:44.370 --> 36:46.679
ON MAX'S BIRTH DAY.

36:46.720 --> 36:48.369
- I THINK I'LL JUST HAVE
A SIP OF COFFEE RIGHT NOW.

36:48.410 --> 36:52.540
OH, NO!
IT'S NOT COFFEE.

36:55.790 --> 36:57.587
- MIXING UP ALL
THOSE INGREDIENTS IN THERE...

36:57.620 --> 36:59.417
- MM-HMM.

36:59.450 --> 37:01.793
- SEEING WHAT COMES OUT.

37:01.840 --> 37:05.241
- ONE PERFECT KID.

37:05.290 --> 37:06.314
- WHO WANTS TO SHAKE?

37:06.360 --> 37:07.804
[children screaming]
HOW DO YOU DO?

37:07.840 --> 37:10.456
HOW DO YOU DO?
HOW DO YOU DO?

37:10.500 --> 37:13.355
[laughter]

37:21.820 --> 37:23.811
- ANDY, THANK YOU VERY MUCH.

37:23.860 --> 37:26.328
YOU REALLY MADE THE PARTY.

37:26.380 --> 37:27.824
IT WAS AMAZING.

37:27.860 --> 37:29.828
- BUGS ARE GREAT.

37:29.860 --> 37:31.487
- YEAH, WELL,
IT WASN'T JUST THE BUGS.

37:31.520 --> 37:32.680
YOU'RE REALLY GOOD
AT WHAT YOU DO.

37:32.730 --> 37:36.621
IT'S ALSO GREAT
THAT YOU ARE DOING SOMETHING

37:36.660 --> 37:37.797
THAT YOU LOVE TO DO.

37:41.390 --> 37:44.939
SORRY, I'M IN YOUR WAY.

37:44.980 --> 37:49.496
UH...

37:49.540 --> 37:51.633
SO YOU REALLY LIKE THIS?

37:51.680 --> 37:54.808
YOUR JOB?

37:54.850 --> 37:57.023
YOUR LIFE?
WHAT YOU DO?

37:59.410 --> 38:01.446
ARE YOU HAPPY?

38:01.480 --> 38:04.825
- YEAH, SOMETIMES.

38:04.860 --> 38:06.896
ARE YOU HAPPY?

38:06.930 --> 38:10.866
- YEAH.

38:10.900 --> 38:13.903
SOMETIMES.

38:16.940 --> 38:18.874
UH, DO YOU WANT ME
TO GIVE YOU A HAND?

38:18.910 --> 38:20.320
- NO, I BREAK DOWN
BY MYSELF.

38:20.360 --> 38:25.559
- OKAY.

38:25.610 --> 38:27.328
- [laughs]

38:27.370 --> 38:28.883
- SO, AS FAR
AS BUG PARTIES GO,

38:28.920 --> 38:30.535
WHERE WOULD YOU RANK
THAT ONE?

38:30.580 --> 38:31.854
- OH, TOP TEN, EASY.

38:31.890 --> 38:33.858
- TOP TEN?
- YEAH.

38:33.890 --> 38:35.471
- HOW MANY BUG PARTIES
HAVE YOU BEEN TO?

38:35.520 --> 38:36.896
- I'VE BEEN TO QUITE A FEW.
- REALLY?

38:36.930 --> 38:38.067
THAT WAS MY FIRST.

38:38.100 --> 38:39.579
- WOW.

38:39.620 --> 38:40.723
- YEAH.

38:40.760 --> 38:41.795
- YOU GOT TO GET OUT MORE.

38:41.830 --> 38:43.934
- I KNOW. I DO.
- HUH.

38:43.970 --> 38:45.551
- I'M MISSING
ALL THESE BUG PARTIES.

38:45.590 --> 38:46.591
- YOU ARE.

38:46.630 --> 38:49.906
[laughter]

38:49.940 --> 38:51.828
WELL...

38:51.880 --> 38:55.907
I GUESS I'LL SEE YOU LATER.

38:55.950 --> 38:57.838
- GOOD NIGHT.

38:57.880 --> 39:02.089
- GOOD NIGHT.

