VERY EASY TO DO, SO...

39:51.970 --> 39:56.145
THAN KS.

39:56.180 --> 39:58.694
OKAY.

40:00.810 --> 40:04.940
- YOU KNOW, UM...

40:04.980 --> 40:08.609
I ACTUALLY THINK
IT WAS GOOD--

40:08.640 --> 40:11.848
EVERYTHING THAT HAPPENED
WITH DREW,

40:11.890 --> 40:13.812
THE FIGHT, THE PUNCH.

40:13.850 --> 40:16.683
YOU KNOW,
YOU WITH HIM,

40:16.720 --> 40:18.028
