40:28.040 --> 40:29.928
- THANKS.

40:29.970 --> 40:33.007
- AMBER MIGHT TAKE
A LITTLE LONGER.

40:33.050 --> 40:34.836
- YEAH.

40:34.880 --> 40:38.976
YOU STILL WRITE SONGS
NOW AND THEN?

40:39.020 --> 40:41.944
- [laughs]

40:41.990 --> 40:44.811
NOT REALLY.
NO. NO.

40:47.610 --> 40:49.919
- YOU SHOULD.
YOU'RE REALLY GOOD AT IT.

40:49.960 --> 40:53.828
- PLEASE.

40:53.860 --> 40:54.827
- OKAY, THANKS.

40:54.860 --> 40:57.829
